Name:Mystic Fox
Desc:The Mystic Fox is part of the werewolf team but does not wake up with the werewolves. The Mystic Fox may wake up every night to check a player's card, but will not see the card. The werewolves will be made aware which player the Mystic Fox has checked and see that player's card. Once per game, the Mystic Fox may decide to become a werewolf permanently.
